        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，都是那些个鸱鸮。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宋公明，他扶危济困隐公曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他两个，他两个俯首低眉哩，要为咱把肝胆效。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱走了半日，肚中又饥又饿，这里有个酒坊儿在此，吃他娘的一饱再走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒保，酒保。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来哉，来哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄土泥墙壁，青标插树梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要害怕，咱是天生的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，天生的这个贼像。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做啥个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃酒的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃酒个，请到里面坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿酒来，拿酒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃酒坐定了，不要这么大惊小怪的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快拿酒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，拿酒来吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人酒那里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这酒淡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放把盐在里头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说酒淡，我说放把盐在里头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我且问你。你这里可有上等的烧刀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上阵的腰刀。我这里没有，到铁匠铺里才有呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "瞎，你不卖那个烧酒吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，是这个烧酒吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有，有，有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，来，来与我小小地取这么一馔来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，小小的取这么一馔来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有，"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。伙计，拿一瓮烧酒来吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人酒那里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打开，打开！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哉，眼睛里着不得灰的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这才是好东西。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人碗大坛子小，放不下的。除非按扁了，才放得下去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪，你那里可有下酒菜吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有鱼，虾，海蜇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多不用，多不用，你拿个猪首来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人又来取笑了。一个猪，只有四只脚，一个头，一根尾巴，哪里有手。若有"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了手，岂不是妖怪了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，不懂咱的话吗？那猪头就是猪首，猪首就是那个猪头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，猪头就是猪首，猪首就是那个猪头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有，有，有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，拿个猪头得来吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，猪头那里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，可要拿刀来切切？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用，呕有拿吃法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪哼吃法？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪开！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人慢慢地吃，啊呦，可要点茶来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪开！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走莫走，啥个茶来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想朝中蔡京、童贯、杨戬、高俅，这班奸贼，若提起。令人可恨！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刮地风） 哎呀，想起那权臣，忒杀个势，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惯纵着心腹贪饕。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那生辰纲，载满珍和宝。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "逐渐渐，是那些，民间的脂膏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只见他收括介，把民财浩。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又见那输运介，把民力抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "入虎穴，把虎子掏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "料不为蝇头激动咱这英豪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，恐怕停住食。打一路消消食哪再吃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哉，客人吃罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这么长，这么粗，一条牛鞭子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，囚囊的，你要呕，你要呕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这球日的还弗晓得呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待咱吃完了酒，再商量。我想生辰纲，不知有多少的官兵护送着哩。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四门子） 算将来此事非关小，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事非关小。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "料区区怎能把党羽招。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "及早向东溪庄保正觅头僚。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "料闻言怒气难消。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生辰纲将将来，轻轻担儿上挑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓霎时间好取如拾草。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，一个甏几乎打碎了，献子底哉，客人可吃了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不吃了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不吃了。算账。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多少？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一壶一坛，一个猪头，共银一两二钱三分四厘半。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有，拿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，这锭银子可要加加。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这么一大锭，还要加，加你娘的鸟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这球日的当真醉了。待我来朦一朦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人还少些。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少多少？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少这么二三厘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，小心牙齿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "造化你了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢客人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒保。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那哼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这里要往东溪村，从哪里走？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "东溪村，出了我家店门，一直碰鼻子就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒保。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那哼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是个好人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是个烂好人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是个好人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "断送一生性有，破除万事无过。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
