    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘唐",
        "朱仝",
        "雷横"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水仙子） 俺，俺，俺，俺可也皮摄交。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎，怎，怎，怎说得不饮饱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早，早，早，早已是醉陶陶。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "强，强，强，强把那村遥绕。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苦，苦，苦，苦那迢迢跋涉儿遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看，看，看，看那牛羊下，日暮林臬。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这，这，这，这渔洲漫漫水畔寂寥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见，见，见，见那夕阳影里个倾颓庙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒涌上来了，这里有所灵官殿在此，不免进去睡他娘一觉再走。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂，刁神。咱刘唐要借你这供桌上，睡这么一觉，你休怪俺！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水仙子） 我暂，暂，暂，暂借宿度今宵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱仝、雷横同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行人赶行人，"
        },
        {
          "character": "雷横",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一程又一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥吓，怎么赶到这里，又不见了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "雷横",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这里有所古庙在此，我们进去看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两廊下——"
        },
        {
          "character": "雷横",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "雷横",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再到大殿上去看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，好一条汉子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "雷横",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看他可有器械？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有器械。"
        },
        {
          "character": "雷横",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "取了他的器械，将他紧紧地绑起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉子醒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 俺酣后醉卧，"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝、雷横",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "醒来吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要搅吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝、雷横",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是什么样人吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘唐 （煞尾） 俺是个海内英雄，"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝、雷横",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "海内英雄，是个强盗了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 休猜作蹬墙穿穴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们绑俺到哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝、雷横",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿你去见晁保正。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，见晁保正？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝、雷横",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后退！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝、雷横",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，好一条汉子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，且住。我正要见晁保正，被这两个狗头绑了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝、雷横",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 好一似失林的昆鸟，"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝、雷横",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱走不动便怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若不走，我就打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "雷横",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我就砍！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘唐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就砍！呔，我把你两个囚囊的，闪开，待咱走，走，走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱仝、雷横",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走，走，走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘唐、朱仝、雷横同下。）"
        }
      ],
